16 Hours Ago Sanwo-Olu assured that the full weight of the law would be brought upon all involved in the murder. The governor commiserated with Bamise’s family, friends and prayed that God would console them. Promising that the deceased would “get the justice she deserves”, Sanwo-Olu said BRT services remained safe despite the condemnable act.